## Deployment

Single-file deployment — replace `CATCH.html` in the repository root. No dependency changes. Azure Static Web Apps (Free SKU) picks up the update automatically on push to `main`.

```
gh release create v2.1 CATCH.html \
  --title "CATCH v2.1" \
  --notes-file CATCH_v2.1_Release_Notes.md
```
